-- programming in Actor Prolog. The program consists only of --
-- the SADT diagram in the IDL format. The source text       --
-- components written in Actor Prolog are connected to the   --
-- program automatically in accordance to the names of       --
-- blocks of the SADT diagram and the #package options       --
-- included into the notes of the blocks of the diagram.     --
-- Actor Prolog translates the diagram into the logic        --
-- program and executes it.                                  --
